  <name>qBit Process Monitor</name>
  <summary>Pause or throttle qBittorrent downloads when specific programs are running</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Monitors running processes on your system and automatically pauses or throttles
      qBittorrent downloads when a matching program is detected. Downloads resume or
      speed limits are restored when the program exits.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pause all torrents or apply speed throttle when matching processes are running</li>
      <li>Configurable process name patterns (substring match)</li>
      <li>Automatic resume/restore when matching processes exit</li>
      <li>Connects to qBittorrent via its Web API</li>
      <li>Built for the COSMIC desktop environment</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
